  "text": [
    "To be blessed",
    "said the old woman",
    "is to live and work",
    "so hard",
    "God\u2019s love",
    "washes right through you",
    "like milk through a cow",
    "To be blessed",
    "said the dark red tulip",
    "is to knock their eyes out",
    "with the slug of lust",
    "implied by",
    "your up-ended skirt",
    "To be blessed",
    "said the dog",
    "is to have a pinch",
    "of God",
    "inside you",
    "and all the other",
    "dogs can smell it"
  ],
  "title": "The Blessing of the Old Woman, the Tulip, and the Dog",
  "year": ""
}